quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  28,12,"Uqbel, Negdel as tid iĂ»Ă»uĂźuven. Tenna: \"ad awen ssekne$ axxam ar awen itkwelfen fellas, u nitni ad as bedden"
  28,13,"Nerra t id i imma s, iwakken ad as kkawent wallen is, ur t$webben, iwakken a pĂ©eĂŽ ar lemĂąahda n Ăebbi d tidep. Maca, tegwti degsen, ur ssinen"
  28,14,"Mi meqqweĂŽ, ittaĂąqel, Nefka yas tussna, Ă»Ă»wab. Akka ay Nepkafi imdanen lĂąali"
  28,15,"Ikcem tamdint, di lweqt ideg stehzan imezda$ is. Iufa n sin irgazen pna$en, yiwen seg uĂȘĂŽum is, wayev seg icenga s. Win n uĂȘĂŽum is, issuter as d afus, mgal win n icenga s. Iwwet it Musa s lbunia, in$a t. Inna: \"ayagi, seg igi n CciĂźan. Neppa, s tidep, d acengu n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ, itellifen"
  28,16,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Nek dense$ iman iw, SemmeĂȘ iyi\". IsemmeĂȘ as. Ih, Neppa IpsemmiĂȘ, IpĂȘunu"
  28,17,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! S l$it iK felli, ur ppili$, d awez$i, si loiha ibe$wviyen"
  28,18,"Iufa d iman is di temdint, iugad, iquĂŽaĂą. Atan a d ipĂąaggiv $uĂŽes, win i s d issutren afus, ass izeryen. Inna yas Musa: \"keĂ§Ă§, s tidep, d im$eĂŽĂŽeq n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ"
  28,19,"Acengu nnsen, mi ib$a a t iwwet, inna d: \"a Musa! Day teb$iv ad iyi ten$ev, akken ten$iv yiwen, ivelli? Teb$iv kan a ppiliv d aqehhaĂŽ di tmurt, ur teb$iv ara a ppiliv seg iĂąaĂŽviyen"
  28,20,"Iusa d urgaz si ĂźĂźerf n temdint, ippazal. Inna d: \"a Musa! S tidep, imvebbĂŽen mlalen $ef loal ik, a k n$en. Effe$, nek, seg wid ik ipweĂ»Ă»in"
  28,21,"Iffe$ segs, iugad, iquĂŽaĂą. Inna: \"a Mass iw! Sellek iyi seg ugdud imednas"
  28,22,"Mi ibbwi tikli ar Madian, inna: \"ahat Mass iw ad iyi Iawi d ubrid umĂąin"
  28,23,"Mi ibbwev s aman n Madian, iufa n arbaĂą n l$aci, la sswan. Iufa, di ĂźĂźerf nnsen, snat n tlawin, ĂźĂźfent lmal nnsent. Inna: \"d acu txeddmemt\"? Nnant ed: \"ur nesswa alamma wexxĂŽen imeksawen. Babat ne$ d am$aĂŽ ameqwĂŽan"
  28,24,"Issew asent, iu$al ar tili, inna: \"a Mass iw! Nek ĂŽe$be$ $ef yal lxiĂŽ, ar iyi d Tessersev"
  28,25,"Tusa t id yiwet segsent, s tikli ikukran, tenna: \"atan ak d issawal baba, a k ikafi imi $ tesswev\". Mi iĂŽuĂȘ $uĂŽes, u iĂȘka yas i ivĂŽan, inna: \"ur ppagwad, tepwasellkev seg ugdud imednas"
  28,26,"Yiwet segsent, tenna: \"a baba! EĂźĂźef it d acrik, ih, yif icriken ik, iohed, muman"
  28,27,"Inna: \"b$i$, nek, ad ak fke$ yiwet si yissi yagi, s cceĂŽt a pxedmev $uĂŽi Ăźam iseggwasen. Ma tessawdev mraw, s leb$i k. Ur b$i$ a k hejjne$. Ad ak ili$, ma Irad Ăebbi, seg iĂąaĂŽviyen"
  28,28,"Irra: \"ayagi, gari yidek. A tin sĂąadda$ ger snat n tallitin, ur ippili felli u$ilif. Ăebbi d Awkil, $ef wayen id nenna"